{"tid":127553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]情侶牽手散步　垃圾車輾壓成永訣","createTime":"2017-02-20T07:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T16:19:36.000Z","uid":32407,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb6906e53fdfc1b548bf9f3a280799736e0d85c","tid":127553,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/bkncn-20170219191151574-0219_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170219%2Fbkncn-20170219191151574-0219_05011_001.html&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0f0bf8a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/bkncn-20170219191151574-0219_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/photo/bkncn-20170219191151574-0219_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170219%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170219191151574-0219_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=9e99bad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n情侶（黃圈示）被垃圾車從後輾過，造成一死一傷。<br />\n<br />\n在車來車往的馬路中央散步是浪漫？還是向「死神」招手？甘肅蘭州市上周三凌晨發生一宗恐怖車禍，一對情侶手牽手在馬路中央的綠化帶旁邊散步，被一輛疾馳駛至的垃圾車從而輾壓，造成男子當場死亡、女子受傷，從此陰陽永隔。<br />\n<br />\n從事發路段的閉路電視畫面所見，該對情侶牽手慢行，男的走在馬路，女的沿綠化帶前行。惟一輛垃圾車突然從後而至，直接將兩人輾壓而過，撞人後還飆前數米才停下。從另一角度的閉路電視畫面顯示，被撞女子被撞飛到綠化帶的草叢，之後能自行站起，似在找尋男友，惟他被輾壓後已當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21ca5d76eece731282d675908ef2cd9f27e62c0","tid":127553,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:37:13.000Z","msg":"司機肯定係單身狗"},{"pid":"376b6dd22fb6ebaac474b5310c730fe80f701e77","tid":127553,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"百份有片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577b3baf1ddc4047275ac80e2b8aea65e6548c31","tid":127553,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017d20eaab856e67c36a8e73ed1f4ee35a7e6bf2","tid":127553,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"行中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fca8aa2adf581b92a4b0d7551730a56cce61f10","tid":127553,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"韓劇式浪漫你識乜野啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}